headline: Diamond Hill Small Cap Strategy Bets on Deeply Discounted Alexandria Real Estate Equities (ARE). Here’s Why
summary: Diamond Hill Capital, an investment management company, released its “Small Cap Strategy” fourth-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
